	<script type="application/json" data-type="svelte-data" data-url="https://community-api.creately.com/community/diagram/imh6s1c01">{"status":200,"statusText":"OK","headers":{"connection":"close","content-length":"9857","content-type":"application/json; charset=utf-8","date":"Mon, 11 Dec 2023 13:00:23 GMT","vary":"Origin","x-powered-by":"Express"},"body":"{\"diagram\":{\"id\":\"imh6s1c01\",\"name\":\"Car Rental System - Flowchart Template \",\"description\":\"Flow of Car Rental System - Flowchart Template\",\"imageURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fimh6s1c01\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fimh6s1c01\",\"owner\":\"Creately Templates\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\"],\"relatedDiagrams\":[{\"id\":\"jgqc1q4r1\",\"name\":\"Nervous System Flowchart \",\"description\":\"Flowchart illustrating the human nervous system. Learn how the nerves and the cells carry messages to and from the brain with this nervous system flowchart.\",\"imageURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fjgqc1q4r1\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fjgqc1q4r1\",\"owner\":\"Creately Templates\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\"]},{\"id\":\"i0u3mxz62\",\"name\":\"Employee Flowchart\",\"description\":\"\\n\\nA Employee Flowchart is a useful tool to assist Human Resources (HR) departments. It provides a visual layout of the employee hierarchy within an organization. It outlines employee job roles, responsibilities, and reporting structures in a clear and straightforward manner. By using a flowchart, HR teams can quickly identify any potential issues regarding employee roles, expectations, and overall communication. It effectively highlights employee roles, allowing HR departments to effectively manage and improve organizational functions.\",\"imageURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fi0u3mxz62\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fi0u3mxz62\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\"]},{\"id\":\"jhsnw9or1\",\"name\":\"Sample flowchart \",\"description\":\"Flowcharts are mostly used to show through shapes and images how a certain process is performed, in a chronological order, from start to finish. Use this editable simple flowchart to start visualizing. Explore more visual frameworks and templates on Creately+ Community Hub. \",\"imageURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fjhsnw9or1\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fjhsnw9or1\",\"owner\":\"Creately Templates\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\",\"flowchart template\",\"process flowchart\"]},{\"id\":\"dKXtbnXS9yq\",\"name\":\"Objections Flowchart Example\",\"description\":\"The Objections Flowchart Example is a visual representation that outlines a systematic approach for addressing and overcoming objections in a structured manner. This flowchart illustrates the step-by-step process of identifying common objections, categorizing them, and providing tailored responses or solutions for each objection type. By following this flowchart, teams can enhance their communication skills, anticipate challenges, and effectively navigate conversations, resulting in improved customer interactions, heightened problem-solving abilities, and ultimately, increased success in addressing objections. \",\"imageURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002FdKXtbnXS9yq\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002FdKXtbnXS9yq\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\"]},{\"id\":\"iun5p3qz\",\"name\":\"SMART Goals ( Flowchart)\\n\",\"description\":\"\\n\\nA SMART Goals Flowchart is a powerful tool for effective management. It is an acronym for Specific, Measurable, Achievable, Relevant, and Time-bound. Each step of the flowchart guides leaders through an organized system for setting and achieving goals. The end result is well-defined objectives that are actionable and on track for success. By breaking down complex tasks into individual steps, managers are able to develop clear strategies for their organization that increase efficiency and performance. With a SMART Goals Flowchart, teams have the necessary tools to make informed decisions and confidently keep their business goals on track.\",\"imageURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fiun5p3qz\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fiun5p3qz\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\"]},{\"id\":\"jhkacrab1\",\"name\":\"Protein Synthesis Flowchart \",\"description\":\"\\n\\nThis protein synthesis flowchart is a great tool for any student learning about protein synthesis. It offers an easy-to-understand visual representation of the process of protein synthesis. From the initial transcription of a gene to the final product of a protein, this flowchart makes it simple for students to learn about protein synthesis. Moreover, this flowchart encourages students to trace the individual steps involved in the creation of a protein, making it an effective way for them to comprehend the complexity of protein synthesis. All in all, this tool can be a great resource for students of all levels learning about biology and biochemistry.\",\"imageURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fjhkacrab1\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fjhkacrab1\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\"]},{\"id\":\"jrsrv16a3\",\"name\":\"Meeting Flowchart Template \",\"description\":\"Flowchart template to map, improve, design and analyze processes during meetings. Use this editable template to customize it to your own needs. Explore more visual frameworks and templates on Creately+ Community Hub.\",\"imageURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fjrsrv16a3\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fjrsrv16a3\",\"owner\":\"Creately Templates\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\",\"flowchart template\"]},{\"id\":\"impu9l3w1\",\"name\":\"Repeat Loop - Flowchart Example \",\"description\":\"Flowchart example for Repeat Loop. The repeat loop will always execute the process part at least once. \",\"imageURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fimpu9l3w1\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fimpu9l3w1\",\"owner\":\"Creately Templates\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\"]},{\"id\":\"KIzBBmUVo7w\",\"name\":\"AI Flowchart\",\"description\":\"Use this AI Flowchart example to efficiently build, validate, optimize, and deploy your machine learning model. The step-by-step process covered in this example provides everything from problem definition and data collection to model validation and hyperparameter tuning. Start streamlining your workflow and stay ahead of the curve with our AI Flowchart today.\",\"imageURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002FKIzBBmUVo7w\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002FKIzBBmUVo7w\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\",\"AI\",\" machine learning\",\" data science\",\" workflow\"]},{\"id\":\"jny57xed8\",\"name\":\"Horizontal Flowchart Template\",\"description\":\"Editable horizontal flowchart template to illustrate process steps. Use Creately to create flowcharts to visualize your processes, systems, and information flows. Explore more visual frameworks and templates on Creately+ Community Hub.\",\"imageURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fjny57xed8\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fjny57xed8\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\",\"horizontal flowchart\",\"process\",\"process mapping\"]},{\"id\":\"hubC3AV7JaY\",\"name\":\"Simple Flowchart\",\"description\":\"A Simple Flowchart template is a straightforward visual tool used to represent a sequence of steps or processes in a clear and easy-to-understand manner. It typically consists of shapes and arrows to illustrate the flow of actions, decisions, or information within a system. This template is an ideal choice for simplifying complex procedures, making it a valuable resource for project planning, process documentation, and problem-solving.\",\"imageURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002FhubC3AV7JaY\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002FhubC3AV7JaY\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\",\"process\",\"planning\",\"flowchart template\"]},{\"id\":\"iq221j5w1\",\"name\":\"Scientific Method - Flowchart Example\",\"description\":\"Scientific method explained using a flowchart. Add or remove steps as required and come up with your own definition of scientific method.\",\"imageURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fiq221j5w1\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fiq221j5w1\",\"owner\":\"Creately Templates\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\",\"scientific method\",\"flowchart-template\"]},{\"id\":\"j20af6gl2\",\"name\":\"Flowchart Template with Multiple Paths \",\"description\":\"Flowchart template with multiple paths, illustrating multiple connective junctions.  Standard flowcharts may contain two paths whereas this template illustrates multiple paths with three endings.\\r\",\"imageURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fj20af6gl2\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fj20af6gl2\",\"owner\":\"Creately Templates\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\"]},{\"id\":\"j71elz4h3\",\"name\":\"Product Launch - Process Flowchart\",\"description\":\"\\n\\nThis presentation will explain the product launch process flowchart and how it can be used to optimize marketing efforts. It will highlight the importance of each phase in launching a product and how it affects the overall impact and reach of the product in the market. The process flowchart and additional resources will provide a visual representation of the steps marketers should take to ensure successful and efficient product launches. Furthermore, this presentation will also provide insight on how to track and measure the success of the product launch in order to make informed decisions for future marketing activities.\",\"imageURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fj71elz4h3\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fj71elz4h3\",\"owner\":\"Library Admin\",\"tags\":[\"flowchart\"]},{\"id\":\"a7NsKKVNvKc\",\"name\":\"Flowchart Template\",\"description\":\"Scientific method flowchart template explaining the scientific research method. Map out your processes and workflows visually with Creately flowchart templates.\",\"imageURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fa7NsKKVNvKc\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002Fa7NsKKVNvKc\",\"owner\":\"Creately Templates\",\"tags\":[\"strategy\",\"process\"]},{\"id\":\"Qbvdi4dvZD5\",\"name\":\"Decision Flowchart Template\",\"description\":\"Decision Flowchart Template (Flowchart)\",\"imageURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002FQbvdi4dvZD5\",\"thumbnailURL\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fsvg.template.creately.com\u002FQbvdi4dvZD5\",\"owner\":\"Lahiru Liyanage\",\"tags\":[]}],\"translations\":{},\"langCode\":\"en\"}}"}</script>
</div>
